    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Imaginary, partly human sea creatures with the head and trunk of a man, usually bearded, and the tail of a fish or cetacean; in Heraldry and elsewhere, often holding a trident and a shell-trumpet.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
